Iran warns that in direct response to the US naval blockade on Iranian oil and gas exports, "other export routes for oil and gas which serve the interests of America and its allies" will also be closed, including the UAE Fujairah pipeline and Saudi East-West pipeline, per Tasnim.

Iran adds "oil and gas exports from the region: either for everyone or for no one."
